      "text": "Single Page Application           Mulit Page Application\n\nSingle Html page                Multi Html page\n\nWithout refreshing entire     For Every click it will \npage it is updating UI         refresh again the page\n\nuser interactions is more     user interactions is less\n\nrequired more database       required less database\n\nrequest are contuie from     request are starting from\nlast point(req are less)       0 everytime(req are more)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Single Page Application           Mulit Page Application\n\nSingle Html page                Multi Html page\n\nWithout refreshing entire     For Every click it will \npage it is updating UI         refresh again the page\n\nuser interactions is more     user interactions is less\n\nrequired more database       required less database\n\nrequest are contuie from     request are starting from\nlast point(req are less)       0 everytime(req are more)",
